title: Alan Moore: Lost Girls (2006) (HC-1280) (FourthMan-DCP)
description:
Single-volume compilation of the FourthMan-DCP three-volume release of Alan "Puts the 'Graphic' into 'Graphic Novel'" Moore's masterwork of erotica, bookended with some exclusive artwork from Pudgy's scan of the 2009 single-volume hardcover edition.

(And if I've now got you wondering why I'm not just uploading the Pudgy scan in its entirety in the first place... that's because the former version is of significantly superior quality to the latter, in terms of definition and saturation and so on.)
